Fisheries (Rock Lobster) Amendment Rules 2019

I make the following rules under the Living Marine Resources Management Act 1995 .

16 September 2019

GUY BARNETT

Minister for Primary Industries and Water

1. Short title
    These rules may be cited as the Fisheries (Rock Lobster) Amendment Rules 2019 .

2. Commencement
    These rules take effect on 1 November 2019.

3. Principal Rules
    In these rules, the Fisheries (Rock Lobster) Rules 2011 are referred to as the Principal Rules.

4.
    The amendments effected by this rule have been incorporated into the authorised version of the Fisheries (Rock Lobster) Rules 2011 .
